  <summary>Professional fragrance composition and formulation tool</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Perfume Composer is a professional application designed for perfumers to create, organize, and manage fragrance formulas with precision. It includes IFRA compliance validation, cost-per-gram calculations, and label printing integration.</p>
    <p>It supports fragrance banks, recipe import/export in JSON and CSV, and automatic label frame management for Bluetooth label printers.</p>
  </description>
